    "Moreover, they primarily leveraged low-level image features and imposed stringent requirements concerning training data and application scenarios.",
    "With the widespread application of deep learning in computer vision, successful advancements have been made in the domain of makeup transfer tasks.",
    "Early on, researchers employed CycleGAN (Zhu et al. 2017a) to implement facial makeup style transfer by treating non-makeup face images and makeup face images as content and style images, respectively.",
    "However, CycleGAN, which primarily focuses on global features, encounters difficulties in achieving satisfactory migration due to the significant variations across different regions of the face.",
    "To address this limitation, makeup transfer can be enhanced by targeting different facial areas individually."
  ],
